org.opends.guitools.controlpanel.datamodel

Class ServerDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.guitools.controlpanel.datamodel.ServerDescriptor

  • public class ServerDescriptor
extends Object
    This is just a class used to provide a data model describing what the StatusPanelDialog will show to the user.
